title: Jackie & Roy with Charlie Ventura's BAnd (1948) Savoy
description:
JACKIE AND ROY JAZZ CLASSICS BY CHARLIE VENTURA'S BAND

1. Euphoria (Charlie Ventura) 
2. F.Y.I. (Charlie Ventura - Roy Kral) 
3. Lady Be Good (G & I Gershwin) 
4. If I Had You (Ted Shapiro - James Campbell - Reginald Connelly) 
5. Deed I Do (Fred Rose - Walter Hirsch) 
6. I'm Forever Blowing Bubbles (Jann Kenbrovin - John William Kellete) 
7. Pina Colada (Charlie Ventura - Roy Kral) 
8. Gone With The Wind (Allie Wrubel - Herbert Magdison) 
9. Once In A While (Bud Green - Michael Edwards) 
10. Lonely Woman (Benny Carter - Ray Sonin) 
11. Sweet Georgia Brown (Ben Bernie - Maceo Pinkard - Kenneth Casey) 

Recorded in Chicago, October, 1948
 
Jackie Cain and Roy Kral with Charlie Ventura and His Orchestra

Norman Faye - trumpet 
Benny Green - trombone 
Charlie Ventura - tenor & baritone sax 
Ben Ventura - baritone sax 
Roy Kral - piano & vocals Gus Cole - bass 
Ed Shaughnessy - drums 
Jackie Cain - vocals 

2000 Savoy
